headline: 3 Reasons CWST is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Casella Waste Systems has gotten torched over the last six months - since May 2025, its stock price has dropped 22.2% to $88.08 per share. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
